Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:26.70,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,And on they echo, the swirls of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:39.90,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,Such blessed happiness they give to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:50.00,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,Proof of a world that will never be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:57.30,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,The priestesses of Tempus Spatium
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:06.00,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,Will rock the cradle until the morning wakes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:13.10,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,Under the Great Mother's care,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:19.70,Lullaby,,0,0,0,,Under white wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We will proceed as planned. Chor Tempest will enter at low altitude, with our speaker cables attached. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission objective is to protect the Ruins from the Alliance between Plumbum and Argentum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:10.14,Titles,,0,0,0,,Funeral Procession
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Her soul was bound by sin. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, through the compassion of Tempus Spatium,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the benevolence of the Holy Land, we forgive and receive her. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was Angulas's body inside that ancient Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She was definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,AA - E - RU ! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They were unable to find so much as a single splinter of bone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She has received the protection of Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For the one departing upon a new journey, we offer a prayer. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A Highland priestess who acted as a covert operative! 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised they would allow her funeral to be held here on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what Her Eminence wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Defence Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of Plumbum and Argentum's new alliance, the Ministry claims that they cannot even risk returning her body. 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite their apparent hostility towards each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly didn't expect the two of them to agree about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind won't blow in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought that you'd start a conversation with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened at the Ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Spring was inside the Ruins, and Onashia was there as well. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This place... this place {\i1}is{\i0} the Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Grandpa said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Angulas, who we thought had been blown up in the explosion, was inside the ancient Simoun. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Angulas went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At the instant the Simoun exploded,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,she went to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Another... world? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally get back to the Arcus Prima,\Nand now all this weird stuff keeps happening! 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Can't we even relax for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no time to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that we're supposed to meet at the Maaju Pool right after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I like doing Maaju, but it sucks to do it just 'cause we're ordered to. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Neviril and Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I guess they got over their differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "got over?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just Neviril being an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Aaeru. What's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Grandpa always said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Grandpa! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as far as I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, you have to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, growing old means that you have to make a few decisions along the way. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you've made those decisions, those possibilities are gone forever. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A Simoun lets you see what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"What's to come?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Another world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he meant by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grandpa always longed to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, is that the reason you didn't want to choose your sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The helical motors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that they manipulate time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always thought that was just a fairy tale,\Ntold to make the Simoun seem sacred. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"I am everywhere, and I am nowhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If Onashia is like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and Angulas was like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Simoun are like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...Limone and Dominura might be too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What we've just discussed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It must remain a secret between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep it a secret, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you go to Angulas's funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"No one from a low-born family like yours can be permitted to attend such a holy ceremony." 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why? Until now, we've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Things change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Central Command is all screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But they even approved the funeral of an enemy priestess, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not the sort of thing I'd expect you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you like Angulas?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I expected at least this much discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only because of the Vice-Chairman's influence that I was able to remain a Simoun sibylla. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vice-Chairman has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's just a regular old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Mamiina, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Living on the {\i1}Messis{\i0} was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the mouse stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All the noble priestesses were happily feasting on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought, "Hah! We're all the same!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We really are different. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Maaju Pool is under the jurisdiction of the Interior Ministry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If the military authorities set foot here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Eminence will—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept my apologies, Minister, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but such a large audience will disturb our prayers. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maaju are not prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're military training, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We would like to see you perform the most powerful Ri Maajon... 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Chor Tempest is capable of drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What beautiful lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dandelion Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't deceive anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's purely for the sake of ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything has gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the right decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...to entrust Neviril to Aaeru as her pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Everything went well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your judgement so unreliable that you'd rather listen to someone who's been asleep? 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking that she needs a nobody like you to protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's damned arrogant of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Neviril... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I've made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were with you—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I've made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dismantle a Simoun."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd hear those words from anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominura...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wapourif, forget about that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my final word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Someone who has nothing to believe in has no firm ground to stand on." 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that {\i1}I{\i0} believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have assigned my maintenance crew to dismantle the ancient Simoun, as you instructed. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismantling a chariot of the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a mortal sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're{\i0} sinful? We're not the ones who defiled the temple of Tempus Spatium with a foreigner's body. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's agenda is to decide what to do about the enemy's airborne base ship. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the ancient Simoun have fallen into the hands of the Highlanders. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be too dangerous to send Chor Tempest on a reconnaissance mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When, might I ask, will it be safe to give them such a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your concern for the well-being of your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if another problem arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be forced to consider your position, Mr. Vice-Chairman. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Sibylla Neviril's pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be Sibylla Aaeru, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Her skills as an auriga are outstanding even among the members of Chor Tempest. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't her grandfather...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, my apologies, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Angulas's funeral is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't she be buried without delay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the Defence Minister's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Defence Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mocking the souls of the dead like this is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your Simoun, you girls are powerless. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be dangerous to ignore the airborne base ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will fly reconnaissance in order to locate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Messis{\i0} will serve as your relay station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on! I thought we finally got away from that mouldy dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my best to accomodate you again, Sibylla-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eww...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And what should we do if we find the base ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you judge that the circumstances—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the circumstances, we should completely annihilate it! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,With the whereabouts of Sibylla Dominura and Sibylla Limone unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we feel it necessary to reorganize the current pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Alti,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Rodoreamon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Mamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Yun, Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you will not be participating in this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—! Why the hell do I have to stay behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She{\i0} is my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand a satisfactory explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, do not cause more trouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Having trouble sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Maaju this afternoon was remarkable. 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you dance with me? Just one song?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but right now I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected to see you stand up for Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't as if I've opened my heart to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But facing Aaeru is like facing Amuria, 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and doing that has forced me to face myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what I was afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was relying too much on everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not let yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rely on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I keep going, there's a whole other world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to see another world, I'll show it to you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Yun is asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might be too nervous to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the pair of the Sibylla Aurea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I always saw that as the quickest way to reach my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly want to be on the same level as the rest of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but my reasons are different now. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly want to be friends with everyone. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So please stop saying "but we {\i1}are{\i0} friends!" and stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little sensitive about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, would you like me to sing you a lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you were singing for Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't. I'm not a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you were taken off the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something that might be the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Promises are meant to be kept.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I.
